Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是我硬求给安排在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为指南手册是总务委员会编排的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是滥用职权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想见委员长的话  去会议室看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不能由你去拜托吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这也是一种办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我对交涉没有太大信心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,由千反田来提出申请  我在一旁帮着说些好话如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,请帮帮我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了  就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看来不是很积极啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个  我更想去做宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才穿成这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是其一  我还有其他的秘策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在文化祭中开展的各项比赛里  以古典文学部的名义参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能取得优异成绩的话  古典文学部的知名度也会上升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是想自己玩得开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}真不愧是福部同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这确实是个好主意  现在确定方针了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,千反田去进行申请新摊位的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,里志负责宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先这么行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  折木同学你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,负责看店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…的确得留个人在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  差不多走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,开幕式的点名就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  就按刚才的任务分配开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,争取多卖一本是一本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,目标是「冰菓」二百本全部卖完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  嘿  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谜题研究社进展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我宣布第五十四届KANYA祭开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  跳过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  转起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是兴奋的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要练练书法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,书法耶  书法哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要练练书法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}好地产好米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的话  留作纪念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去不行  绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,筑波岭峰上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,春尽夏已至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,启程道扬镖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}神出鬼没！！  欢迎初学者  百人一首部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来一战吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,久违…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去不行  绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}总务委员会本部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,总算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好美的画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…请问有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我来找总务委员长的田名边同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是田名边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊  那么…请为古典文学部增加销售摊位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,国际活动部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,国际活动部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我是古典文学部部长千反田爱瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请为古典文学部增加销售摊位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么突然地来申请  我也没法立即同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  等等  那只是从原则上讲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么缘由的话  可以说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得福部同学好像说交涉时会来帮忙来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我说  能踩油门就走呗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂  不成  不成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是危险人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,原因就是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这的确很辛苦啊  我也想帮帮你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  每个部都有难处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不能只对古典文学部特殊照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果请其他部在他们摊位帮忙代售古典文学部社刊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不会干涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好方法啊  我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,各位早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  伊原  你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,河内学姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,连短刀都配备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是塑料做的仿制品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要是鞋子也下番功夫就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么嘛  到头来不也还是Cosplay吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明明之前那么反对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要是一开始就按河内说的做该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,早啊  汤浅学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,早安  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,花钱了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只是买了腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有发票的话记得给我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,能在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不好开口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托在这儿代售《冰菓》什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你这扮的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个  是芙洛露哦  你知道《第11人》吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哎  我都没听说过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是挺久以前的SF漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是部名作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下次借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  要借什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,漫画啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  大家加油干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请问  已经开店了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一号客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看店万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先把肯定能卖出去的写上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,根据现状考虑  古典文学部四人每人买两本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后加上顾问老师以及保存用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,共计12本是一定能卖出的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,其实  只卖掉这些也不算少了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:21:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs18}歌曲为：圣堂教父（The Gospellers）的\N《独自一人》（ひとり）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c000000\bord0\shad0\frz214.358\pos(378,265)}目标  200部全部卖完！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:21:06.04,InsertJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}うたがってた三月 涙が急にこぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:20.32,InsertJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}許し始めた五月　わだかまりも夏に溶けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:25.98,InsertJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}たった一つのこと　約束したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:33.46,InsertJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}これから二度と　離さないと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:39.17,InsertJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}たった一人のため　歩いてゆくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:45.23,InsertJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}あなたに二度と　悲しい歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:51.28,InsertJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}聴こえないように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:21:06.04,InsertCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}曾经怀疑的三月 泪水潸然而下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:20.32,InsertCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}开始谅解的五月 芥蒂也随夏天融化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:25.98,InsertCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}和你的约定只有一件　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:33.46,InsertCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}那就是永远不再分开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:39.17,InsertCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}只为你一人　朝前而行　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:45.23,InsertCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}不会再让你听见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:51.28,InsertCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}悲伤之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}咦  有谁看见我的苹果汁了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}没看见耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}唉  我还一口没喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}那张纸是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}不  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}比起这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕  好困
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}朋克文化：起源于1970年代的一种亚文化。最早源起于音乐界，\N后逐渐转换成一种整合音乐、服装与个人意识主张的广义文化风格。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  朋克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.36,0:22:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是朋克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是干嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啥都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊不  在卖社刊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这全都是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那卖我一本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  客人？是客人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我得热情一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  根本没笑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,老…老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个  能让我看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个真好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是服装研究会的  正准备做流行时装表演
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.16,0:23:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可是正装系的胸袋配饰让我给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这个真的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,反正已经是废品了  请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那我给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们表演的优先券
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,带着这个来服装研究会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就会为你配搭最棒的服装
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要去也只有里志会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.85,0:23:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不  那家伙也有他的执着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,总之是卖出一本了
